library(FactoMineR)
library(factoextra)

data(poison)
poison.active <- poison[,5:15]
res.mca <- MCA(poison.active,graph=F)    #graph=TMCA
fviz_screeplot(res.mca,addlabels=T,ylim=c(0,45))    #addlabels

fviz_mca_ind(): Graph of individuals

fviz_mca_var(): Graph of variables

fviz_mca_biplot(): Biplot of individuals and variables

fviz_mca(): An alias of fviz_mca_biplot()

fviz_mca_biplot(res.mca,repel=T,ggtheme=theme_minimal())    #repel avoid text overlapping; ggtheme

Warning: ggrepel: 30 unlabeled data points (too many overlaps). Consider increasing max.overlaps

fviz_mca_var(res.mca,repel = TRUE,ggtheme = theme_minimal())

fviz_mca_ind(res.mca,col.ind = "cos2",#
             gradient.cols=c("#00AFBB", "#E7B800", "#FC4E07"),#
             repel=T,ggtheme=theme_minimal())

Warning: ggrepel: 25 unlabeled data points (too many overlaps). Consider increasing max.overlaps
